NLquery: For each Internet Service(sid), find the most frequently used version among all Base Models that utilize it.
LLM_returned_SQL_query: SELECT sid, version, COUNT(*) AS usage_count FROM ModelServices GROUP BY sid, version ORDER BY usage_count DESC;

NLquery: For each Internet Service(sid), find the most frequently used version among all Base Models that utilize it.
Find all the Internet Service(sid) that are utilized by every Base Model built by the agent creator user_iuwrh.
LLM_returned_SQL_query: SELECT ms.sid FROM ModelServices ms JOIN BaseModel b ON ms.bmid=b.bmid WHERE b.creator_uid='user_iuwrh' GROUP BY ms.sid HAVING COUNT(*) = (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM BaseModel WHERE creator_uid='user_iuwrh');

Find all customized models(mid) that do not appear in model configurations.
LLM_returned_SQL_query: SELECT mid FROM CustomizedModel WHERE mid NOT IN (SELECT mid FROM ModelConfigurations);
